check.label: a test completes
check.vc2: teststr('eOptions','emailtestdone'):$e if ($e) then eOptions[$e]='' IPeOptions=eOptions endif

check.label: reports
check.vc2: teststr('eOptions','emailreport'):$e if ($e) then eOptions[$e]='' IPeOptions=eOptions endif

check.label: a test fails
check.vc2: teststr('eOptions','emailtestfail'):$e if ($e) then eOptions[$e]='' IPeOptions=eOptions endif

check.label: spectral plots
check.vc2: teststr('eOptions','emailplot'):$e if ($e) then eOptions[$e]='' IPeOptions=eOptions endif

textmessage.set: atcmd('VPscheduledtests','list'):$timestamp,$user if ($user='') then $VALUE='No schedule active' else $VALUE='Tests scheduled to run on '+$timestamp endif
